Title: Jeajoon Ryu concerto per violoncello ed orchestra by Lahti Orchestra, Arto Noras and Okko Kamu
Description: Jeajoon Ryu's cello concerto was performed at Lahti. It was special concert for Maestro Okko Kamu's 70th Years Anniversary concert and perform by Maestro Arto Noras. It also world première concert of 3rd edition.

Title: Jean Sibelius: Press Celebrations Music - Okko Kamu, Lahti Symphony Orchestra
Description:
Sibelius Festival 2012 concerts free at http://www.classiclive.com/Concerts

Lahti Symphony Orchestra

Sibelius Festival 2012 Day 2

Okko Kamu, conductor

Jean Sibelius: Press Celebrations Music, JS 137

Preludio
Tableau 1: Väinämöinen delights Nature, and the peoples of Kaleva and
Pohjola, with his song
Tableau 2: The Finns are baptized
Tableau 3: Scene from Duke Johan's Court
Tableau 4: The Finns in the Thirty Years War
Tableau 5: The Great Hostility
Tableau 6: Finland Awakes

The Lahti Symphony Orchestra´s Sibelius Festival, under the baton of Okko Kamu, the orchestra´s principal conductor and the festival´s artistic director, took place on 6th-9th September 2012. The festival´s theme was ´Sibelius - patriot and mystic`. 

Recorded at Lahti Sibelius Hall Finland, 7th September 2012
